reviewText: Not a very good script, but entertaining. I like the Lindy Hop Dance Scene at the end.

Amber Kuo is one of my favorite actress and I have seen and enjoyed a number of her movies such as "Channel X", "Invincible Shan Boa Mei" and "Love Forward" which was very excellent. This talented actress has such a sweet voice like a little girl's voice in a woman's body. I have been waiting for more releases that have her in it.
